source.name: Colorado Plateau Rapid Ecoregion Assessment Change Agents - Climate Change - Long-Term Potential For Change
source.description: This map shows long-term potential for climate change, which was calculated using a logic model to integrate the factors of:  vegetation change summer & winter temperature change annual precipitation change runoff change.
